OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Former England striker and broadcaster 
OL,6, Eni Aluko has criticised Elon Musk's X 
OL,7, social network for allowing people to  
OL,8, "vomit their hatred unchecked".        
OL,10,FAluko, who faced a wave of abuse after 
OL,11,Fex-footballer Joey Barton attacked her 
OL,12,Fpunditry, told the BBC that black women
OL,13,Fare being systematically targeted.     
OL,15,FThe BBC tracked down one of the trolls 
OL,16,Fmotivated by Barton's posts.           
OL,18,FHe said he shared hateful comments     
OL,19,Fabout women such as Aluko because they 
OL,20,Fare "just an easy target".             
